<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/19(Thu)6Healthy Ways to Manage Your Coronavirus Anxiety/Weirded Out by Working From Home?7Tips to Make It Easier-Nikki]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=373&amp;p=390#p390"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">*** Removal Notice ***<br />Thursday gathering of Royal English Club is relocated to Ikari 怡客咖啡, 台北市中正區衡陽路116號</span><br /><br /><br />&lt;Session 1&gt;<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/health/wellness/a31478108/coronavirus-anxiety-tips/">https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/health ... iety-tips/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Have you ever experienced anxiety? How did you know it’s anxiety?<br />2. What emotions are you （or people around you ）going thorough with coronavirus? How are you coping with those negative emotions?<br />3. Share your experience of coping with uncertainty/ unwanted change.<br /><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />&lt;Session 2&gt;<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog/tech-support/202003/weirded-out-working-home-7-tips-make-it-easier">https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/blog ... -it-easier</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. How has coronavirus affected your life/work, if any?<br />2. What do you think about working at home? What are the possible pros and cons?<br />3. What can you do to boost your immune system?<br /><br /><br />Extended reading: “ How to keep your workplace clean- and yourself healthy-during the novel coronavirus outbreak”<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/11/health/how-to-clean-work-desk-coronavirus-wellness-trnd/index.html">https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/11/health/h ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2020/03/11/health/how-to-clean-work-desk-coronavirus-wellness-trnd/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2020/03/11/heal ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />====================================================================================================<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 pm-7:30 pm Free talk<br />7:30 pm-8:10 pm Session 1 discussion<br />8:10 pm-8:40 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 pm-8:45 pm Break time &amp; Group picture<br />8:45 pm-9:15 pm Session 2 discussion<br />9:15 pm-9:30 pm Presentation<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Tue Mar 17, 2020 9:36 pm</p><hr />
